short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generate TypeScript types from JSON data

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An efficient tool for effortlessly converting JSON data or JS object into TypeScript types! This extension is designed to help developers quickly generate accurate TypeScript type definitions, saving time and boosting development efficiency.

Features:
1️⃣Paste JSON data directly and generate the corresponding TypeScript types with one click
2️⃣Supports complex nested objects and arrays
3️⃣Intuitive interface and easy to use
4️⃣Saves time and reduces manual errors

Whether you're a front-end developer or a full-stack engineer, this extension can be your go-to assistant for daily development. Download now and experience efficient type definition generation!
